          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_Profile_SetProperties",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to manage user profile properties within an ASP.NET application. It handles the creation and updating of user profiles, including setting property names and values, both in string and binary formats. The procedure ensures that the application and user exist in the database, updating or inserting records as necessary."
        }
      ]
